| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5050 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c6adc5b3-4e9a-55eb-bf85-3217f46a5915"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
